name: Trump tariffs
summary: President-elect Donald Trump announced plans to impose new tariffs on goods imported from Mexico, Canada, and China on his first day in office. This move has sparked concerns about the potential impact on trade and industries, as well as the potential for a trade war with other countries. Mexico, Canada, and China have all expressed opposition to the proposed tariffs, with China warning that "no one will win a trade war." The tariffs could affect a wide range of products, including steel, aluminum, and agricultural goods. Economists are predicting that the tariffs could lead to higher prices for consumers and businesses, and could disrupt supply chains. The move is also seen as a protectionist measure aimed at protecting American jobs, but critics argue that it will ultimately harm the economy. Trump's incoming "border czar" has also promised to secure the southern US border, further escalating tensions with Mexico.

A trade proposal involving Antetokounmpo to a Western Conference superteam has also emerged, adding to the speculation surrounding his future. In addition, he is listed as questionable for an upcoming game against the Bulls, with further updates on his injury status pending. name: Champions League
summary: The UEFA Champions League is undergoing a format expansion for the 2024/25 season, with the number of teams increasing and the abolishment of the away goal rule. In recent updates, Bayern Munich emerged victorious against a 10-man Paris Saint-Germain despite Kim Min-jae's first-half goal. The Champions League matchday 5 schedule, live stream, and storylines are available on Paramount+. Sports Illustrated provides predictions for matchday 11/26. NBC Sports offers the league table standings for the 2024-25 season. Al Jazeera English reported on the thrilling 3-3 draw between Manchester City and Feyenoord. ESPN provides injury and suspension news, predicted lineups, and fantasy updates for the Champions League. CNET offers livestream options for Manchester City vs. Feyenoord. Eurosport COM covers the latest updates on the Bayern Munich vs. Paris Saint-Germain match, while Forbes reports on Barcelona's lineup changes for their match against Brest.
